Class MoveInPointFigurePairs

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.MoveInPointFigurePairs
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.util.Map.Entry<Point,IFigure>>

    public class MoveInPointFigurePairs
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<java.util.Map.Entry<Point,IFigure>>
    This class has the data on which positions change for a move and it has the information over the next game state. Furthermore he has the information if a figure was hit or a pawn was set.
